description: Try our easy to follow Chocolate Chia Brownies recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Chocolate Chia Brownies Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Add the flour, cocoa, walnuts and sugar to the mixing bowl with the chia seed paste, mashed potato, light olive oil and melted chocolate, and lastly fold through the egg whites. Spread the mixture across a 30x20cm baking tray lined with baking paper and bake for 20-25 minutes, cut into squares and store in air tight containers.
